# Updating AGENTS.md for TECHNICAL.md files

Whenever a new TECHNICAL.md file is created in any module directory, you MUST:

1. Update `AGENTS.md` to include the new TECHNICAL.md file in the "Current TECHNICAL.md files" section
2. List the file using the format: `- \`modules/[module-name]/TECHNICAL.md\` - Brief description of what the module does`


## Example

If you create `modules/newmodule/TECHNICAL.md`, add this line to AGENTS.md:

```
- `modules/newmodule/TECHNICAL.md` - Technical documentation for the NewModule module
```

This ensures that all technical documentation is discoverable and documented in the main AGENTS.md file.
